		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>The BEST way to play a wiz from ground up...From 1-9, solo...find a spot with blues near a safe place to med, root, burn, rinse, repeat...<br><br>At 10, the mob hp start going up, and you end up wasting too much time running for zones with the root routine.&nbsp;&nbsp;You need a friend.  Just one.  Go to a popular zone, like ECommons, and advertise for a partner, not a group.  2 of any class, when one is a wiz, can get exp 1.5 times faster both soloing.  Best possible is a shaman or druid, but I had great success from 11 to 20 with a monk buddy. EC from 10-12, wisps in WC from 12-13, then move to the Oasis at 14 for sick exp off of the caimen and crocs...</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
